Riga Free Port has implemented all recommendations suggested by State Control regarding Krievu Island project.
The Riga Free Port administration has implemented all five recommendations by the State Control (SC) concerning the transfer of port activities away from the city center within the project "Infrastructure development of the Krievu Island Port", the company informed portal Diena.lv.
The project approval is expected at the nearest Riga Free Port's board meeting.
