The museum's then-director Vilhelms Purvitis was one of the promoters of the monument.
The newest initiative might thus be considered its logical continuation.
I have constant remorse: what about Vilhelms Purvitis, where shall we enshrine his name?
"But if you, Mr Ameriks, promise to think about that"... said Lace.
As reported, the building of the National Museum of Art, after a major reconstruction and modernization, re-opened this May.
Reconstruction of VEF Culture Palace will finally start this week.
